## Limitations
This report is limited by the availability of up-to-date data and the rapidly evolving nature of renewable energy technologies. Some sources may not reflect the latest advancements or regional variations in renewable energy implementation. Additionally, the focus was primarily on English-language sources, which may not capture the full global perspective on the issue.